Port listing:
    * ss -at ---> for TCP protocol
    * ss -au ---> for UDP protocol
    * ss -aut ---> for both TCP and UDP
    * sudo lsof -i -P -n | grep LISTEN

History of commands:
    * history

History of mysql commands:
    * cat ~/.mysql_history

Preview of networking interfaces and addresses;
    * ip addr

Connecting to MySQl server:
    * mysql -h serverAddress -u username -ppassword

Services commands:
    * systemctl status service
    * systemctl restart service


